\c 59
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukukhululwa ezitheni
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Alitashethi. IMikitami kaDavida. USawuli esethume, njalo balinda indlu ukumbulala
\p
\v 1 Ngikhulula ezitheni zami, Nkulunkulu wami\x + Hlab. 143.9. 2 Sam. 22.49.\x*, ungimise ngaphezu kwabangivukelayo\x + Hlab. 143.9. 2 Sam. 22.49.\x*\x + Hlab. 17.7. 139.21.\x*.
\v 2 Ngikhulula kubenzi bobubi\x + Hlab. 94.4.\x*, ungisindise ebantwini abomele igazi\x + Hlab. 5.6.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Ngoba, khangela, bacathamela umphefumulo wami\x + Hlab. 10.9.\x*; abalamandla bayangihlanganyela\x + Hlab. 56.6.\x*, kungekho siphambeko sami njalo kungekho sono sami, N\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Sam. 24.11. Hlab. 7.3.\x*.
\v 4 Ngaphandle kwecala bayagijima bezilungisa\x + 1 Sam. 24.11. Hlab. 7.3.\x*. Vuka, ungisize, ubone\x + Hlab. 35.23.\x*.
\v 5 Wena-ke, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wamabandla, Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + Hlab. 80.4. 84.8.\x*; vuka ukuze uhambele zonke izizwe\x + Hlab. 35.23.\x*, ungahawukeli lamunye wabakhohlisayo ebubini. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 25.3.\x*.
\v 6 Bayabuyela kusihlwa, behlaba umkhulungwane njengenja, bezingelezela umuzi\x + 59.14. Hlab. 22.16.\x*.
\v 7 Khangela, bempompoloza ngomlomo wabo\x + Hlab. 145.7.\x*, inkemba zisendebeni zabo\x + Hlab. 57.4.\x*, ngoba \add bathi\add*: Ngubani ozwayo\x + Jobe 22.13.\x*?
\v 8 Kodwa wena, N\nd kosi\nd*, uzabahleka\x + Hlab. 2.4.\x*, uzaziklolodela zonke izizwe\x + Hlab. 2.4.\x*.
\v 9 \add Ngenxa\add* yamandla akhe ngizalindela kuwe, ngoba uNkulunkulu uyinqaba yami.
\v 10 UNkulunkulu womusa wami uzangandulela\x + Hlab. 21.3. Mat. 17.25.\x*; uNkulunkulu uzangenza ngibone \add isiloyiso sami\add* ezitheni zami\x + Hlab. 54.7.\x*.
\v 11 Ungazibulali, hlezi abantu bakithi bakhohlwe; uzizulazulise ngamandla akho\x + 59.15. Nani 32.13. Gen. 4.12-15.\x*, uzehlisele phansi\x + Hlab. 55.23. 56.7.\x*, wena sihlangu sethu, Nkosi\x + Hlab. 84.9.\x*.
\v 12 \add Nge\add*sono somlomo wazo, \add ng\add*elizwi lendebe zazo\x + Zaga 18.7.\x*, kazibanjwe ekuzigqajeni kwazo, langenxa yokuhlambaza lokuqamba amanga ezikukhulumayo.
\v 13 U\add zi\add*qede ngokuthukuthela, u\add zi\add*qede zingabi khona, ukuze bazi ukuthi uNkulunkulu uyabusa koJakobe\x + Hlab. 83.18.\x*, kuze kube sekupheleni komhlaba. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 22.27.\x*.
\v 14 Kababuyele-ke kusihlwa behlaba umkhulungwane njengenja, bezingelezela umuzi\x + 59.6.\x*.
\v 15 Bona kabazulazulele ukudla\x + 59.11. Hlab. 109.10. Jobe 15.23.\x*, nxa bengasuthanga kabalale\x + Eks. 16.7. Nani 16.11.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Kodwa mina ngizahlabelela ngamandla akho; yebo, ngizahlabelela kakhulu ekuseni ngomusa wakho; ngoba ube yinqaba yami\x + 59.9.\x* lesiphephelo sami\x + 2 Sam. 22.3.\x* ngosuku lokuhlupheka kwami\x + Hlab. 66.14.\x*.
\v 17 Mandla ami, ngizahlabelela kuwe, ngoba uNkulunkulu uyinqaba yami\x + 59.9.\x*, uNkulunkulu womusa wami\x + 59.10. Hlab. 144.2.\x*.